# Cobalt Design System

You are working in the Cobalt Design System — a Lit + Shoelace web component library with React, Vue, and Angular wrappers. Monorepo managed with pnpm workspaces.

## Packages

- `@cobalt/components` — Lit web components (packages/components/)
- `@cobalt/tokens` — Design tokens via Style Dictionary (packages/tokens/)
- `@cobalt/react` — React wrappers (packages/react/)
- `@cobalt/vue` — Vue wrappers (packages/vue/)
- `@cobalt/angular` — Angular wrappers (packages/angular/)
- `@cobalt/icons` — Icon set (packages/icons/)
- `@cobalt/docs` — VitePress docs site (packages/docs/)

## Component Patterns

Components register `<co-*>` custom elements. Import per-component entry points:

```js
import '@cobalt/components/co-button';  // Good
// import '@cobalt/components';          // Bad — registers everything
```

### Framework usage:

- **Web Component:** `<co-button variant="primary">Save</co-button>`
- **React:** `import { Button } from '@cobalt/react'` → `<Button variant="primary">Save</Button>`
- **Vue:** `import { CoButton } from '@cobalt/vue'` → `<CoButton variant="primary">Save</CoButton>`
- **Angular:** `import { CobaltButtonModule } from '@cobalt/angular'` → `<co-button variant="primary">Save</co-button>`

## co-button

Variants: `primary`, `secondary`, `danger`, `ghost`. Sizes: `sm`, `md`, `lg`.
Props: `variant`, `size`, `disabled`, `loading`, `type`, `href`, `target`.
Events: `co-focus`, `co-blur`. Slots: default, `prefix`, `suffix`.

## Design Tokens

CSS custom properties with `--co-` prefix. Import `@cobalt/tokens/css/tokens.css`.

```css
background: var(--co-color-primary-600);
padding: var(--co-spacing-4);
border-radius: var(--co-radius-md);
box-shadow: var(--co-shadow-md);
font-family: var(--co-font-family-sans);
```

Always use semantic tokens over hard-coded values or primitives.
Categories: color, spacing, radius, shadow, font, z-index, transition, breakpoint.

## File Naming (kebab-case)

- `co-{name}.ts` — component source
- `co-{name}.styles.ts` — component styles
- `co-{name}.test.ts` — unit tests
- `co-{name}.a11y.test.ts` — accessibility tests

## Conventions

- Custom events: `co-` prefix (e.g., `co-change`, `co-focus`)
- CSS custom properties: `--co-{component}-{property}-{variant}-{state}`
- TypeScript: strict mode, prefer `interface`, avoid `any`
- Properties: `reflect: true` when affecting styling/a11y
- Commits: Conventional Commits — `feat(co-button): add ghost variant`
- Tests: unit + a11y tests, 90% coverage, use @open-wc/testing + axe-core

## Reference Files

- Component APIs: `packages/components/custom-elements.json`
- All tokens: `packages/tokens/dist/tokens.json`
- Coding standards: `packages/docs/contributing/coding-standards.md`
